 which a concept was deprecated. Concepts that are deprecated but not inactive can still be used, but their use is discouraged, and they should be expected to be made inactive in a future release. Property type is dateTime. Note that the status property may also be used to indicate that a concept is deprecated</td></tr><tr><td>retirementDate</td><td>retirementDate</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#retirementDate</td><td>dateTime</td><td>The date at which a concept was retired</td></tr><tr><td>niveau</td><td>niveau</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#niveau</td><td>integer</td><td>Permet d'indiquer le niveau hiérarchique du code</td></tr></table><p><b>Concepts</b></p><p>This case-insensitive code system <code>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r395-engagement</code> defines the following codes dans une hiérarchie Is-A:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Définition</b></td><td><b>Parent</b></td><td><b>dateValid</b></td><td><b>dateMaj</b></td><td><b>dateFin</b></td><td><b>status</b></td><td><b>niveau</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">ARRT<a name=\"tre-r395-engagement-ARRT\"> </a></td><td>Arrêté</td><td/><td/><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td>active</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">CONV<a name=\"tre-r395-engagement-CONV\"> </a></td><td>Convention</td><td/><td/><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td>active</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">DISP<a name=\"tre-r395-engagement-DISP\"> </a></td><td>Dispositif</td><td/><td/><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td>active</td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">LABL<a name=\"tre-r395-engagement-LABL\"> </a></td><td>Label</td><td/><td/><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td/><td>activ